description: [``botocore``] AWS Elemental MediaConvert SDK has added support for Kantar SNAP File Audio Watermarking with a Kantar Watermarking account, and Display Definition Segment(DDS) segment data controls for DVB-Sub caption outputs.
[``botocore``] This release contains updates for Amazon ECS.
[``botocore``] This release updates create-nodegroup and update-nodegroup-config APIs for adding/updating taints on managed nodegroups.

[``botocore``] Add three new optional fields to support filtering and configurable sub-band in WirelessGateway APIs. The filtering is for all the RF region supported. The sub-band configuration is only applicable to LoRa gateways of US915 or AU915 RF region.

[``botocore``] This release adds new APIs to associate, disassociate and list related items in SSM OpsCenter; and this release adds DisplayName as a version-level attribute for SSM Documents and introduces two new document types: ProblemAnalysis, ProblemAnalysisTemplate.
[``botocore``] Amazon Kinesis Analytics now supports ListApplicationVersions and DescribeApplicationVersion API for Apache Flink applications
[``botocore``] Adds paginator to multiple APIs: By default, the paginator allows user to iterate over the results and allows the CLI to return up to 1000 results.
